node.title: Serious injuries after motorbike crash in Waikato's Gordonton
node.description: The collision involved a single motorbike.
node.content: ["A motorbike crash in the rural Waikato town of Gordonton has caused serious injuries.\n", "Police say the collision happened about 9:20am and involved a single motorbike,", "\"Indications are there are serious injuries,\" a police statement said.", "Police said the area near the intersection of Broadley Downs and Gordonton Rd is closed as a result of the crash.\u00a0", "Travel delays are expected.", "\"Motorists are asked to avoid the area,\" police said."]
